---
title: Thai Pork Curry with Sweet Potato and Baby Corn
description: This curry packs a real nutritional punch! Sweet potatoes are full of beta-carotene and vitamin C, but the really interesting ingredient is Thai basil. For centuries, it’s been used in Ayurvedic medicine to ward off everything from headaches, fever, respiratory problems and even anxiety.
